data.description: Welcome home to this meticulously maintained gem.  Seller is offering a $5,000 credit towards buyers closing cost.  Step inside and be greeted by two separate living areas, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The open kitchen seamlessly flows into the dining area and living room, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere that is ideal for family gatherings.  An added bonus, the Owned Solar Panels, power this home.  Refrigerated air to keep you cool during those hot summer months.  Downstairs boasts beautiful tile flooring, adding a touch of elegance to every step you take.  Upstairs, you'll find gorgeous wood flooring that adds warmth and character to the space.
